queries.sql: SELECT `projects`.*, CONCAT(customers.first_name, " ", customers.last_name) AS customer_name, CONCAT(customers.address1, ", ", `customers`.`address2`, ", ", customers.city_state) AS customer_address, `customers`.`zipcode`, `customers`.`phone` AS `contact_info`, `customers`.`created_at` AS `customer_created_at`, `users`.`first_name` AS `assigned_to_name` FROM `projects` JOIN `customers` ON `customers`.`id` = `projects`.`customer_id` LEFT JOIN `users` ON `users`.`id` = `projects`.`assigned_to` ORDER BY `projects`.`created_at` DESC
